    <p>The gas cleared, and Travis disintegrated. Zc suddenly realized that he, the unnamed ferret’s sister, and everyone else had become anime-tized. The kid said, “Ferret-girl! You are the chosen one! This world is the fabrication of bored humans! Now you must return to your drawing!” Terry and Z were not ready to accept that and decided to fight back.</p>
