    <p>The unnamed ferret’s sister then exclaimed, “MINE!” and glomped onto Z. Terry couldn’t help but think that it wasn’t worth the trouble. He said, “Now that I think about it…I’m not sure if you’re really worth the trouble. ^_^;;”</p>
